  <h2>Mulvane Sits Between Two Counties</h2>
  <p>The county line split is something sellers in Mulvane need to be aware of. Depending on which side of town your property sits on, probate, tax records, and closing processes may run through Sedgwick County in Wichita or Sumner County in Wellington. We deal with both regularly and know which title companies handle cross-county transactions smoothly.</p>
  <p>Mulvane also has a fair number of rural residential properties — larger lots, sometimes with outbuildings or agricultural history. These can be tricky to sell traditionally because the buyer pool is smaller. Cash buyers like us are often the most straightforward path.</p>
